        "content": "<p>I'd like suggestions for a shorter abbreviation for ·, like in <code>(· + ·)</code>.  Unfortunately, \\cdot is already taken for ⬝ (which is a different unicode symbol).  I'm getting tired of typing \\centerdot.</p>",
        "id": 238053225,
