        "content": "<p>In Emacs it's</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Text only\"><pre><span></span><code>             to input: type \"\\centerdot\" or \"\\cdot\" or \"\\dot\" or \"\\.\" with Lean input method\n</code></pre></div>",
